ntact us.</p><p>Best regards,<br><strong>{{myCompanyName}}</strong><br>Email: {{myEmail}}<br>Phone: {{myPhone}}<br>Website: <a href=\"{{myWebsite}}\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#0056b3;\">{{myWebsite}}</a><br>Address: {{myAddress}}<br>GST: {{myGst}} | PAN: {{myPan}}</p></div>",
